In the [[:en:Meiji era|Meiji era]], under the [[kazoku]] system's {{ill|Clan system (Kazoku)|ja|宗族制 (華族)|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Clan system (Kazoku)|qq=}}, families of Shoban lineage were classified as "Gaibetsu" ("foreign origin").
